-- Nigeria Forecasts Growth of 7.75% for 2010, Finance Minister Aganga Says
-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 2010-10-25T11:11:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/nigeria-forecasts-growth-of-7-75-for-2010-finance-minister-aganga-says.html
Nigeria forecasts economic growth of
7.75 percent this year, Finance Minister Olusegun Aganga said at
a conference in the capital, Abuja, today.  Gross domestic product growth in the first half was 7.4
percent, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
